OL,3,CPub body calls for beer duty cut amid
OL,4,Cpotential outdoor smoking ban
OL,6,FA body representing British pubs has
OL,7,Fcalled for a raft of tax cuts ahead of
OL,8,Fthe October Budget, following recent
OL,9,Freports suggesting the Government
OL,10,Fcould ban smoking in beer gardens.
OL,12,FThe British Beer and Pubs Association
OL,13,Fsaid it wants a cut to beer duty,
OL,14,Fadding that pubs currently make an
OL,15,Faverage of 12p profit on every pint of
OL,16,Fbeer once taxes and costs have been
OL,17,Fdeducted.
