OL,3,CPub body calls for beer duty cut amid
OL,4,Cpotential outdoor smoking ban
OL,6,FIt comes alongside fresh research by
OL,7,FOxford Economics, a think tank, which
OL,8,Fsuggests pubs contributed #34.4
OL,9,Fbillion to the economy in 2022, the
OL,10,Fmost recent year on record, and #17.4
OL,11,Fbillion in tax.
OL,13,FBut Emma McClarkin, chief executive of
OL,14,Fthe BBPA, said the sector is
OL,15,F"shouldering multiple taxes and costs
OL,16,Fthat are squashing growth and could
OL,17,Flead to businesses failing".
