OL,3,CPub body calls for beer duty cut amid
OL,4,Cpotential outdoor smoking ban
OL,6,FThe number of pub closures increased
OL,7,Fto 80 per month over the first three
OL,8,Fmonths of 2024, up by 51% compared
OL,9,Fwith the same period last year,
OL,10,Faccording to official Government data
OL,11,Ffor England and Wales.
OL,13,FIn August, Sir Keir Starmer said the
OL,14,FGovernment would "take decisions" on a
OL,15,Fpotential outdoor smoking ban in an
OL,16,Feffort to curb preventable deaths and
OL,17,Falleviate pressures on the NHS.
