OL,3,CPub body calls for beer duty cut amid
OL,4,Cpotential outdoor smoking ban
OL,6,FIndustry leaders have warned that the
OL,7,Fproposed plans to ban outdoor smoking,
OL,8,Fincluding in beer gardens and outside
OL,9,Fstadiums, would be another "nail in
OL,10,Fthe coffin" for pubs and bars.
OL,12,FAccording to leaked proposals seen by
OL,13,FThe Sun newspaper, the indoor smoking
OL,14,Fban could be extended to cover other
OL,15,Flocations including small parks,
OL,16,Foutdoor restaurants and hospitals.
